Package hu.bme.mit.theta.solver.smtlib.dsl.gen

Interface SMTLIBv2Listener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SMTLIBv2BaseListener
    public interface SMTLIBv2Listener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by SMTLIBv2Parser.
